desc: Plus Size Kweens provides clothing options for plus size women up to a size 3x. All clothing is trendy and affordable. New looks are coming to the website soon. See products from pants to maxi dresses.

layout.text: I've always been a plus size women even when I was younger and finding clothes, shoes, and lingerie that made me feel sexy and comfortable was sometimes difficult. I learned very quickly that being comfortable in your own skin and displaying that confidence was the key to making sure everyone knew that I was here and not going anywhere. My lingerie line focus on providing my fellow Kweens with amazing products that hugs every kruvy at cost efficient price so every Kween can feel beautiful.
